---
// Recruitment call-to-action at the bottom of the home page.
// Edit this file to change the joining text or link destination.
---

<section id="join" class="py-16 px-4 bg-navy-dark text-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in joining?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
      Great! We need your contribution to the team, even if you don&rsquo;t want
      to build robots, or even if you don&rsquo;t have any prior experience.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/contact/"
      class="inline-block bg-gold text-navy-dark font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors"
    >
      Get in touch &rarr;
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
